# The vault — heavy reference ore (~767MB), crawler direct-access, on disk only.
# Manifest-primary: recoverable from the original sub-repos via vault/MANIFEST.md; not versioned here.
# Ignore the vault's CONTENTS (not the dir itself) so git still descends and the
# two negations below can re-include the committed routing docs.
vault/*
# ...but the routing docs for the vault MUST commit so a cold agent can route there.
!vault/CONTEXT.md
!vault/MANIFEST.md

# mdBook build output
library/completed/sans-python/book/

# Language artifacts
**/.venv/
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
**/node_modules/
**/target/

# Model weights / large binaries (per the M1 reproducibility lesson)
*.pt
*.pth
*.safetensors
*.gguf

# Local agent + tooling state
.claude/
.gstack/

# Logs & OS cruft
*.log
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.codex-*.txt
.roadmap*.png
__pycache__/
.pytest_cache/
.env
